File::Find::Rule::SAUCE - Rule to match on title, author, etc from a file's SAUCE record

This module will search through a file's SAUCE metadata (using File::SAUCE) and match on the
specified fields.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


DEPENDENCIES

The module requires the following modules, available on CPAN:

  File::SAUCE
  File::Find::Rule
  Test::More

